A nice followon of this for the obsessive archiver is:

Procmail:
.procmail/rc.mail
	<snip>
	:0:
	* ^Subject.*\[ILUG\]
	:ilug-`date "+%m-%Y"`
	<snip>

and Mutt:
.muttrc:
	mailboxes =ilug-`date "+%m-%Y"` 

does mean threads get broken at the start of the month though :(

